The paper proposes a framework for distributed online data classification, which involves machine learning algorithms and big data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with data processing and analysis, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
